product_name: Soleus Chicked Digital Watch - Women's - 2012 Overstock
long_description: The Soleus Chicked women's digital watch features a thin, flexible wristband and easy-to-read display so you can see exactly what time it is when you blow by the competition. Watch functions include dual display, time and date, 30-lap memory, stopwatch, 2 alarms and dual time zones. 5-interval timer allows you to set workouts with variable intervals so you can mix long and short intervals without resetting your watch. Backlight illumination helps you operate the watch during pre-dawn or dusk workouts. Soleus Swift women's digital watch is water-resistant to 100m. Overstock.
